{"tid":547330,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"『極短叫春文』","createTime":"2018-02-01T10:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T10:37:18.000Z","uid":16042,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea55e7b0a05e859d1654ca49c3b64c4ef52762ee","tid":547330,"uid":16042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"生病了，我們會去找醫生；心病了，我們又能找誰呢？<br />\n<br />\n世間上有沒有一種藥，吃過以後可以把你一生中最最最後悔的事情就此抹去。<br />\n<br />\n都說往事如煙，怎麼我一直困在這團煙霧裡，逃不開、吹不散，<br />\n無論遠處或是眼前，始終只得這一片煙霧瀰漫，都燻得我看不見別的風景了。<br />\n<br />\n每一次以為走出去了，待回過神來以後才發覺眼底又開始變濛了，一滴、兩滴，滂沱大雨。"},{"pid":"70b7cb7b8b6dcbd0574237ea506cbcb9ff89aaca","tid":547330,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"不開心便找醫生"},{"pid":"3cbbbf5768a062f9342eeda0673502b12476c8eb","tid":547330,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1TNW-kN1aTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1TNW-kN1aTY&d=skPcRPOHki9g%2B54DNKJBatU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7bc42d39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1TNW-kN1aTY</a>"}]}